<!-- Name and description of this project: How should it be listed in
    textgridrep.org/projects
-->
    <name>Corpus poético de Fernando de Herrera</name>
    <description>This corpus contains the complete poetic works of the 16th-century Spanish writer Fernando de Herrera (1534–1597), with the sole exception of his Latin poems. </description>

<!-- Use this if you want to upload an avatar (logo) for your project.
    Avatar is a TextGrid URI pointing to a published image, it will be
    shown in 250x250px
